<h3><a id="drugref" name="drugref"
href="http://www.drugref.org/">Drugref.org</a></h3>

<p>
drugref.org is a collaborative attempt at creating and maintaining an
independent free pharmaceutical reference database.

<br />
The principles include
<ul />
<li /> continuous peer review of all information
<li /> independence of industry
<li /> independence from funding related constraints
<li />  independence from countries, health systems, and languages
</ul>
<br />
This project depends on active community contributions. Anybody with a
medical , pharmaceutical or biochemical degree is welcome to
contribute. 
<br />
</p>

